  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Bethany believes that adoption is the best way to achieve the goal of permanency for children who lack parental care. We believe that foster care provides the intermediary step that allows time for families to receive thorough and professional support before they adopt a child domestically.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="3">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Children, families, child welfare workers.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Recruit, train, license and support local foster and adoptive parents; assessment of children; case management/supervision; support after placement; advocacy; activities intended to develop the child welfare infrastructure.</narrative>
